data.description: Beautifully maintained one level living townhome in Wallburg Landing. The large kitchen has plenty of counter space and cabinets. The end unit has great light and privacy. The primary bedroom has a large ensuite bath complete with a garden tub, shower, and double sinks. The custom closet has great storage. Enjoy your evenings in front of the gas fireplace in the living area. (TV and sound bar convey).   All appliances, including the washer and dryer will remain. Don't miss this great unit.
